{"tid":2310022,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"Jupas以外 大家仲有冇咩其他選擇....","createTime":"2020-12-03T03:23:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T05:35:57.000Z","uid":193380,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"0dbd8141b12981d10d2e08f0b31413574470b82e","tid":2310022,"uid":193380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T03:23:54.000Z","msg":"有時覺得香港比起外國好似少好多出路<br />\n好似每個人都係向住醫生律師條路行<br />\n大家都好似為左份工，而冇左自己興趣咁<br />\n定係喺香港就一定要隨波逐流呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea9d6839203e9e789a8dc1229e317300fabb28e2","tid":2310022,"uid":104865,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"0dbd8141b12981d10d2e08f0b31413574470b82e","tid":2310022,"uid":193380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T03:23:54.000Z","msg":"有時覺得香港比起外國好似少好多出路<br />\n好似每個人都係向住醫生律師條路行<br />\n大家都好似為左份工，而冇左自己興趣咁<br />\n定係喺香港就一定要隨波逐流呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T03:26:01.000Z","msg":"唔明你講咩 jupas for entry大學 同出路有咩關係"},{"pid":"1921a322e38c21b312f000fdac790d231c5c823f","tid":2310022,"uid":155674,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea9d6839203e9e789a8dc1229e317300fabb28e2","tid":2310022,"uid":104865,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"0dbd8141b12981d10d2e08f0b31413574470b82e","tid":2310022,"uid":193380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T03:23:54.000Z","msg":"有時覺得香港比起外國好似少好多出路<br />\n好似每個人都係向住醫生律師條路行<br />\n大家都好似為左份工，而冇左自己興趣咁<br />\n定係喺香港就一定要隨波逐流呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T03:26:01.000Z","msg":"唔明你講咩 jupas for entry大學 同出路有咩關係"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T03:30:07.000Z","msg":"我估佢係想講jupas嘅科好唔廣泛<br />\n我9up 可能有d人對飛機維修好有興趣<br />\n但jupas係冇得讀<br />\n所以好似少左choice咁"},{"pid":"0ceb3996b0c20fa109f314f86bf98c011223feec","tid":2310022,"uid":86224,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T03:35:08.000Z","msg":"其實香港畢業都仲有好多出路<br />\n簡單d講, APA 都係其中一個出路啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人生只活一次<br />\n點解要活喺人地嘅mindset入面<br />\n巴打 共勉之"},{"pid":"bd4d525ed9235b009b46b15b9fd26f2df8356f2a","tid":2310022,"uid":66049,"like":21,"dislike":11,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T03:38:25.000Z","msg":"讀science -&gt; 乞食<br />\n讀文科 -&gt; 乞食<br />\n讀IT -&gt; IT狗<br />\n讀商科 -&gt; 銀行櫃枱/保險狗<br />\n讀nursing/醫 -&gt; 準備引入支那醫護<br />\n讀法律 -&gt; on9仲信香港法治<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n老實講而家咁嘅時勢<br />\n出去讀野雞仲好過喺香港讀<br />\n喺香港讀越讀越迷失<br />\n畢業都係變社畜俾政府強姦你份糧做明日大嶼<br />\n點解唔襯後生俾機會自己出去探索下<br />\n<br />\n不過窮撚出唔到國都係算數<br />\n留返喺香港學蝗語早日加入發展大灣區逗返幾千蚊人工卑賤度日"},{"pid":"0b4c8d97abc5d53482e1ce23e72e8a94b7e7ff7f","tid":2310022,"uid":10274,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T03:58:33.000Z","msg":"樓主又唔洗咁灰心<br />\n其實香港都仲有好多唔同嘅出路架<br />\n你上E-APP / VPET個網都有好多course可以揀<br />\n揀一科自己鍾意嘅都好緊要架<br />\n星期五好似仲有個VPET facebook live <br />\n你可以上去睇下幫唔幫到自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6464d281c175b64c38391dc4bc5eb332a5233cf0","tid":2310022,"uid":86224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b4c8d97abc5d53482e1ce23e72e8a94b7e7ff7f","tid":2310022,"uid":10274,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T03:58:33.000Z","msg":"樓主又唔洗咁灰心<br />\n其實香港都仲有好多唔同嘅出路架<br />\n你上E-APP / VPET個網都有好多course可以揀<br />\n揀一科自己鍾意嘅都好緊要架<br />\n星期五好似仲有個VPET facebook live <br />\n你可以上去睇下幫唔幫到自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"cited